# Reports Directory
# This directory stores all generated reports from security assessments
# 
# Report formats:
#   - .txt : Plain text reports
#   - .json : JSON format for programmatic parsing
#   - .html : HTML reports with formatting
#
# File naming convention:
#   {tool_name}_{timestamp}.{format}
#   Example: port_scan_20240101_120000.txt
#
# Reports are automatically organized by date in the filename
# Clean up old reports periodically to save disk space
